snippet.title: (NO EAS) Carrollton, TX - Texas AMBER Alert - 03/03/2021
snippet.description:
A day after the previous AMBER Alert, another AMBER Alert. 

https://mesonet.agron.iastate.edu/wx/afos/p.php?pil=CAECRP&e=202103031459

BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED
CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY
TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY
RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE CORPUS CHRISTI TX
859 AM CST WED MAR 3 2021

THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS
DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY.

THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT
NETWORK

THE CARROLLTON POLICE DEPARTMENT IS SEARCHING FOR ROSEMARY LEE
SINGER, WHITE, FEMALE, 10 YEARS OLD, MARCH 20 2010, 5 FEET 02 INCHES,
75 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, BROWN EYES, WEARS GLASSES AND WAS LAST SEEN
WEARING A DARK BLUE JACKET RED AND GRAY SHIRT WITH UNKNOWN WRITING,
DARK BLUE PANTS, WHITE/PURPLE SHOES.

POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR RONALD LEE SINGER, WHITE, MALE, 35 YEARS OLD,
OCTOBER 21 1985, 5 FEET 10 INCHES, 235 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, HAZEL EYES
AND GRAY SHIRT, BLUE BANDANA AS A MASK, IN CONNECTION WITH HER
ABDUCTION.

THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A BLACK, 2020 MITSUBISHI OUTLANDER WITH TEXAS
LICENSE PLATE NUMBER N L Z 4 2 0 5. THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM
IN CARROLLTON, TX.

LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THIS CHILD TO BE IN GRAVE OR
IMMEDIATE DANGER. 

IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE
CARROLLTON PD AT 972-466-3333.

NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS CARROLLTON PD AT 972-834-4880.  END OF
MESSAGE.

$$

"Leopard Print Elevator" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
